channel.title: Need help to install project v6
channel.description:
[glow=red,2,300]Project v6 > I need help to install.[/glow]
Hello how do i install project v.6 ? i need compile ? Im using Moparscape 3.1 w/Aryan
When i compile project v.6 i get thesse error: *Javac is not a internet command,externt command,program or commandfile. push a free button for continu*
sry for bad english but i get a swedish text in that error ... im swedish so ..
anyway when i start moparscape 3.1 w/aryan
and i let it load ..... then i press start new server. nothing happend i just get error in running bot :
[img]http://img219.imageshack.us/img219/9397/errorcu3.jpg[/img]
So id youre know how to fix could you ? maybe just need a compiled file ....

item.title: Need help to install project v6
item.dc:creator: @madmax40 madmax40
item.description:
@madmax40 wrote:

you do need to compile , right click your compile file and put this:

@echo off
COLOR 08
title slave scape compiler
“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_07\bin\javac.exe” -cp . *.java
“C:\Program Files\Java\jre1.5.0_07\bin/java.exe” server
pause
